      "bookmarkId": "39980443_118_1428-1492",
      "chapterUid": 118,
      "range": "1428-1492",
      "markText": "我们倾听他们，是为了构建出自己的答案，而不是听了他们的话以后，马上就按他们说的去做，好像自己是只无助的羔羊，或者是个牵线的木偶。",
      "totalCount": 21312,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=118&rangeStart=1428&rangeEnd=1492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=118&rangeStart=1428&rangeEnd=1492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_123_1898-1958",
      "chapterUid": 123,
      "range": "1898-1958",
      "markText": "我们最常见的倾向就是只愿听那些价值观倾向和我们相似的人的话，我们需要下大力气去抵制这种倾向。我们必须要与这种倾向做斗争。",
      "totalCount": 12720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1898&rangeEnd=1958",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1898&rangeEnd=1958"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_118_1132-1226",
      "chapterUid": 118,
      "range": "1132-1226",
      "markText": "专家们多多少少给我们提供了合情合理的观点，为我们做出深思熟虑的决定提供了材料。但是我们自己必须要做能工巧匠，对那些观点和主张加以剪裁、取舍，将它们整合成自己的决定，这样才能做个有主见的人。",
      "totalCount": 10332,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=118&rangeStart=1132&rangeEnd=1226",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=118&rangeStart=1132&rangeEnd=1226"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_122_917-984",
      "chapterUid": 122,
      "range": "917-984",
      "markText": "弱势批判性思维是利用批判性思维来捍卫自己当前的信念。强势批判性思维是利用批判性思维来评价所有的断言和信念，尤其是对自己的信念加以评价。",
      "totalCount": 8481,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=122&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=984",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=122&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=984"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_123_1064-1129",
      "chapterUid": 123,
      "range": "1064-1129",
      "markText": "为了让你更熟悉价值观这个概念，请你先写下自己的一些价值观。注意尽量不要写一些具体的人名，也不要写一些可以触摸到的物体或具体的行动。",
      "totalCount": 7425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1064&rangeEnd=1129",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1064&rangeEnd=1129"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_122_1099-1187",
      "chapterUid": 122,
      "range": "1099-1187",
      "markText": "弱势批判性思维的目的就是坚决抵制和驳倒那些不同的观点和论证。将把那些意见和你不一样的人驳得哑口无言、乖乖认输作为批判性思维的最终目标，会毁掉批判性思维潜在的人道和进步性的特征。",
      "totalCount": 6372,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=122&rangeStart=1099&rangeEnd=1187",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=122&rangeStart=1099&rangeEnd=1187"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_125_1774-1825",
      "chapterUid": 125,
      "range": "1774-1825",
      "markText": "当一个科学家有了一个想法时，他的第一步不是走出去为自己的想法寻找证据，而是思考想法中每一个可能的错误。",
      "totalCount": 5928,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=125&rangeStart=1774&rangeEnd=1825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=125&rangeStart=1774&rangeEnd=1825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_117_2377-2467",
      "chapterUid": 117,
      "range": "2377-2467",
      "markText": "乔纳森·海特(Jonathan Haidt)把我们对情感的依赖描述为一头发怒的大象沿着乡间一路蹂躏肆虐，而我们的理智则如同一个弱小的骑手，竭尽全力想要控制住这头大象狂热的撒野行为。",
      "totalCount": 5811,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=117&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=117&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_123_1433-1479",
      "chapterUid": 123,
      "range": "1433-1479",
      "markText": "你可以问问自己，你希望自己的朋友都是些什么样的人，你希望自己的孩子被培养出什么样的行为准则。",
      "totalCount": 5670,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1433&rangeEnd=1479",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=123&rangeStart=1433&rangeEnd=1479"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_121_738-773",
      "chapterUid": 121,
      "range": "738-773",
      "markText": "如果读者始终依赖海绵式思维，那么最后读到的内容是什么，他就会相信什么。",
      "totalCount": 5253,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=121&rangeStart=738&rangeEnd=773",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=121&rangeStart=738&rangeEnd=773"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_119_550-624",
      "chapterUid": 119,
      "range": "550-624",
      "markText": "批判性思维鼓励你倾听他人，向别人学习，同时掂量别人所说的话，看看它们的分量如何。如此，你将了解到我们必须要依赖他人，但又不能来者不拒，必须做出选择。",
      "totalCount": 5244,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=119&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=119&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_119_433-485",
      "chapterUid": 119,
      "range": "433-485",
      "markText": "我们必须要理性地掌控自己的信念和结论。与之相对的选择是，谁是我们最后遇到的人，我们就甘愿做谁的精神奴隶。",
      "totalCount": 5112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=119&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=119&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_116_995-1041",
      "chapterUid": 116,
      "range": "995-1041",
      "markText": "仅仅因为我想得出一个特定的结论，就认为我掌握的事实与你掌握的事实等价，这是最低劣的智力欺诈。",
      "totalCount": 4890,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=116&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=116&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_134_2122-2164",
      "chapterUid": 134,
      "range": "2122-2164",
      "markText": "我们常常会误解所读到的文章或所听到的言论的含义，因为我们总以为词语的含义都显而易见。",
      "totalCount": 4607,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=134&rangeStart=2122&rangeEnd=2164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=134&rangeStart=2122&rangeEnd=2164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_121_1502-1587",
      "chapterUid": 121,
      "range": "1502-1587",
      "markText": "淘金式思维最重要的特点就是互动式参与，即作者和读者之间、演讲者和听众之间展开的对话。一个会思考和判断的人愿意赞同别人的观点，但他首先得为自己的问题找到一些令人信服的答案。",
      "totalCount": 4464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=121&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=121&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1587"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_130_4967-4980",
      "chapterUid": 130,
      "range": "4967-4980",
      "markText": "切记！评价之前要先等一等。",
      "totalCount": 4428,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=130&rangeStart=4967&rangeEnd=4980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=130&rangeStart=4967&rangeEnd=4980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_117_940-978",
      "chapterUid": 117,
      "range": "940-978",
      "markText": "1)想要说服我们相信某件事的人，总是会向我们解释照他们说的那样做的种种弊端。",
      "totalCount": 4400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=117&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=978",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e6832d3072620d9be68aabf?chapterUid=117&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=978"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39980443_144_1532-1596",
      "chapterUid": 144,
      "range": "1532-1596",
      "markText": "价值观假设会随着情境的改变而改变，它们在一种情况下适用，可一旦规定性论题的具体条件发生改变，我们就有可能出现非常不同的价值倾向。",
      "totalCount": 4392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39980443&chapterUid=144&rangeStart=1532&rangeEnd=1596",
